{"tid":1976850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有個錯誤觀念 好早已經俾人植入咗我地心中","createTime":"2020-04-17T13:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T00:02:36.000Z","uid":320471,"like":41,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"934a4a156f835928e5fbab3b44e9447ab6585570","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"就係 白警<br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單 警察 政府都深知道<br />\n警隊有白警 但佢地有咩辦法處理呢<br />\n好簡單 借我地隻手做<br />\n建立一個觀念 「有白警一早辭咗職啦」<br />\n令到「白警」兩邊唔係人 更加抵受唔到壓力<br />\n真係辭職 警察就成功迫走「二五仔」<br />\n<br />\n好老實 我相信老豆搵仔做到今日咁<br />\n都有部分功勞係黎自白警<br />\n我亦聽聞 真係有手足俾白警放走咗<br />\n<br />\n其實去到呢刻 觀念已經植入得太心<br />\n覺得「白警」on9嘅歡迎任屌我<br />\n<br />\n而真係相信有白警嘅留低句加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地身在曹營<br />\n心理質素其實要控制得好好"},{"pid":"269a995e5f1503a9265a838b52743b67a0cdd028","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:46:57.000Z","msg":"植入得太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b5d80c15a055ef7accf06bd5e6f6235a32f8be","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"當然我諗白警係少於一成<br />\n但都相信有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c3a4fefef76ff6cfa64c1d228571b95984f884","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"唔係重要post<br />\n推一兩下好了"},{"pid":"033062e82b93aa496bdaad5fa33e80a2906b7d98","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"推多下了"},{"pid":"cab45e5e8bdc6208fe2d0067c2951afbcea44f68","tid":1976850,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"79b5d80c15a055ef7accf06bd5e6f6235a32f8be","tid":1976850,"uid":320471,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"當然我諗白警係少於一成<br />\n但都相信有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g